resume_data:
Job Description: Front End Engineer (2 Years of Experience)
Tech Solutions, San Francisco, CA, USA
About Us
At Tech Solutions, we are on a mission to build products that solve complex problems and improve people’s
lives. We are seeking a talented Front End Engineer to join our dynamic team in San Francisco.
Job Description
We are looking for a Front End Engineer with at least 2 years of experience in developing scalable and
user-friendly web applications. The successful candidate will be proficient in modern JavaScript frameworks
and libraries, HTML, CSS, and responsive design principles. This role will contribute significantly to the
creation and implementation of user interfaces for our web applications.
Responsibilities
•Develop new user-facing features using modern JavaScript frameworks like React.js, Vue.js, or Angu-
lar.js.
•Build reusable code and libraries for future use.
•Ensure the technical feasibility of UI/UX designs.
•Optimize application for maximum speed and scalability.
•Assure that all user input is validated before submitting to back-end services.
•Collaborate with other team members and stakeholders.
Requirements
•2 years of experience as a Front End Developer or similar role.
•Proficiency in web markup, including HTML5, CSS3.
•Knowledge of modern JavaScript programming and experience with libraries like jQuery.
•Familiarity with modern front-end build pipelines and tools.
•Experience with popular front-end frameworks (such as React, Vue, or Angular).
•Familiarity with code versioning tools such as Git.
•Degree in Computer Science, Engineering, or a related field.
1 Benefits
•Competitive salary package.
•Health, dental, and vision insurance.
•Retirement savings plan.
•Professional development opportunities.
•Flexible work hours.
Tech Solutions is proud to be an equal opportunity employer. We celebrate diversity and are committed
to creating an inclusive environment for all employees.
How to Apply
To apply, please submit your resume and a brief explanation of your relevant experience to hiring@techsolutions.com .
